  </div>
  <div class='row well'>
    <h3><%= link_to('Posts', posts_path) %></h3>
    <p>Test inline TeX math rendering. Uses <%= link_to('KaTeX', 'https://github.com/Khan/KaTeX') %> and <%= link_to('ExecJS', 'https://github.com/rails/execjs') %>.<p>
  </div>
  <div class='row well'>
    <h3><%= link_to('Products', products_path) %></h3>
    <p>Test stripe checkout and have multiple buttons on same page. Uses <%= link_to('Stripe', 'https://github.com/stripe/stripe-ruby') %>.<p>
  </div>
</div>